- The chosen CD (the crystalline, punch‑restored mastering candidate) matches the core, non‑negotiable items on my list: it explicitly preserves transients, restores punch, offers tight syncopated drums and locked bass interplay, and delivers tape‑like warmth. Those are exactly the attributes I said I prioritize for immediate rhythmic attack and collectible CD energy. 
